Package eu.cqse.check.matlab

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InconsistentFunctionAndFilename
    Checks that a name of a function is consistent with the name of the file in which the function is defined.
    MatlabCheckUtils
    Utility class for Matlab checks.
    MatlabFunctionDeclaration
    Represent a function declaration in matlab and provides useful methods.
    MatlabFunctionParameterCountCheck
    Checks that a function name does not have more than a fixed number of input parameters.
    MatlabUnwantedFunctionCallsCheck
    Checks that unwanted method calls are not used.
    NoEval
    Checks for statements that use the eval function.
    NoIfComplexCheck
    Checks for if statements with a complex condition.
    NoIfZeroCheck
    Checks for if statements with the condition being the 0 constant.
    NoSwitchWithoutOtherwiseCheck
    Checks for switch statements without otherwise condition.
